    <sec sec-type="Main text" id="SECID0EHH">
      <title/>
      <p>On p. 81 the header for the new species reads <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Megastigmus</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">pistaciae</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Roques &amp; Copeland sp. n.</p>
      <p>The CORRECT species name is <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Megastigmus</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">ozoroae</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Roques &amp; Copeland sp. n. The name was misspelled when the PDF file was generated.</p>
